    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Herculi Invicto <lb n="2"/>pro salute <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratoris</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>iti</ex></expan> Aeli Antonini <lb n="4"/>Hadriani <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> Pii <lb n="5"/>et Aureli Veri <expan><abbr>Cae</abbr><ex>saris</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>vet</abbr><ex>erani</ex></expan> et <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>ives</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>R</abbr><ex>omani</ex></expan> et Bessi <lb n="7"/>consistentes <lb n="8"/>vico Quintio<lb break="no" n="9"/>nis auditorio <lb n="10"/>restituto <expan><abbr>cur</abbr><ex>am</ex></expan> a<lb break="no" n="11"/>gentibus Sulpi<lb break="no" n="12"/>cio Narcisso <lb n="13"/>et Derzeno Aul<lb break="no" n="14"/>upori magistra<lb break="no" n="15"/>tis <note>sic</note> et Cocceio Pho<lb break="no" n="16"/>ebo quaestore <lb n="17"/>sigillum posuerunt
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Mittelteil eines Altars oder einer Statuenbasis. Hedera in Z. 6. (B): IScM I: Z. 3: Ael(i) Antonin(i); Z. 5: Caes(aris); Z. 15/16: Phoe/bo.</p>
            </div>
